# Office Green — Plant Pals Operations & Training Plan

**Type:** Academic Capstone — Google Project Management Certificate
**Methodology:** Agile & Waterfall
**Year:** 2025-2026

## Project Overview
End-to-end project management of a new corporate plant delivery 
service — supply chain setup, software integration and employee 
training program.

